---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms & Conditions | Stockifi"
  description="The terms that govern your use of Stockifi, covering access, billing, data handling, and what you can expect from us as a customer."
>
  <div class="legal-hero">
    <div class="legal-container">
      <p class="legal-label">Legal</p>
      <h1>Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="legal-body">
    <div class="legal-container">

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>Applicability</h2>
        <p>These terms and conditions outline the rules and regulations for using Stockifi's services. By accessing our website, mobile application, or any other Stockifi service, you accept these terms and conditions in full. Do not continue to use Stockifi if you do not agree to all of the terms stated on this page.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>Definitions</h2>
        <p>The following terminology applies to these Terms and Conditions and all Agreements:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>"Client," "You," and "Your"</strong> refer to you, the user of our services.</li>
          <li><strong>"The Company," "We," "Our," and "Us"</strong> refer to Stockifi.</li>
          <li><strong>"Party," "Parties"</strong> refer to both the Client and Stockifi.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>All terms refer to the offer, acceptance, and consideration of payment necessary to provide our services in the most appropriate manner, subject to the prevailing laws of the Netherlands.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>Cookies</h2>
        <p>We use cookies to enhance your experience on our platform. By accessing our services, you agree to the use of cookies in accordance with Stockifi's Privacy Policy.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>License</h2>
        <p>Unless otherwise stated, Stockifi and/or its licensors own the intellectual property rights for all materials on our platform. You may access these materials for your own personal use, subject to the following restrictions:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>You must not republish, sell, rent, or sublicense material from Stockifi.</li>
          <li>You must not reproduce, duplicate, or copy material from Stockifi.</li>
          <li>You must not redistribute content from Stockifi.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>User-Generated Content</h2>
        <p>Where our platform allows users to post opinions or information, Stockifi does not filter, edit, or review user-generated content before it appears. Such content reflects the views of the person posting it. Stockifi is not liable for any damages or expenses resulting from user-generated content.</p>
        <p>Stockifi reserves the right to remove any content deemed inappropriate, offensive, or in violation of these Terms.</p>
        <p>By posting content on our platform, you confirm that:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>You hold all necessary licenses and consents to post it.</li>
          <li>The content does not infringe on any third-party intellectual property rights.</li>
          <li>The content does not contain defamatory, offensive, or unlawful material.</li>
          <li>The content will not be used for solicitation or unlawful commercial activities.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>You grant Stockifi a non-exclusive license to use, reproduce, and edit your content in any form or media.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>Hyperlinking</h2>
        <p>Certain organizations — including government agencies, search engines, and news organizations — may link to our platform without prior written approval. We will consider other link requests on a case-by-case basis. If you are interested in linking to our platform, please contact us with the relevant details.</p>
        <p>You may not create frames around our pages without prior written permission.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>Content Liability</h2>
        <p>We are not responsible for content that appears on external websites linking to our platform. By linking to our website, you agree to protect us against all claims arising from your website. No links to our platform should appear on any site containing libelous, obscene, or otherwise unlawful content.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>Your Privacy</h2>
        <p>Please read our <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a> to understand how we collect and protect your data.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>Reservation of Rights</h2>
        <p>We reserve the right to request the removal of any links to our platform, and to amend these terms and conditions at any time.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
        <p>To the maximum extent permitted by applicable law, we exclude all representations, warranties, and conditions relating to our platform and its use. Nothing in this disclaimer will:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Limit or exclude liability for death or personal injury.</li>
          <li>Limit or exclude liability for fraud or fraudulent misrepresentation.</li>
          <li>Limit any liabilities in a way not permitted under applicable law.</li>
          <li>Exclude any liabilities that may not be excluded under applicable law.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>As long as our services are provided free of charge, we will not be liable for any loss or damage of any nature.</p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Hero */
  .legal-hero {
    padding: var(--space-96) var(--space-32) var(--space-64);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .legal-label {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-body-sm);
    font-weight: var(--fw-medium);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--primary-light);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: var(--text-h1);
    font-weight: var(--fw-semibold);
    line-height: var(--lh-h1);
    color: var(--foreground);
    max-width: 640px;
  }

  /* Body */
  .legal-body {
    padding: var(--space-64) var(--space-32) var(--space-96);
  }

  .legal-container {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Sections */
  .legal-section {
    padding-bottom: var(--space-48);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-48);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .legal-section:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: var(--text-h6);
    font-weight: var(--fw-semibold);
    color: var(--foreground);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }

  p {
    font-size: var(--text-body-lg);
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--muted-foreground);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }

  p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  ul {
    margin: var(--space-8) 0 var(--space-16) var(--space-24);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-8);
  }

  li {
    font-size: var(--text-body-lg);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--muted-foreground);
    padding-left: var(--space-8);
  }

  strong {
    color: var(--foreground);
    font-weight: var(--fw-medium);
  }

  a {
    color: var(--primary-light);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    text-decoration-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--primary-light) 40%, transparent);
    transition: text-decoration-color 0.2s;
  }

  a:hover {
    text-decoration-color: var(--primary-light);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .legal-hero {
      padding: var(--space-64) var(--space-24) var(--space-48);
    }
    .legal-body {
      padding: var(--space-48) var(--space-24) var(--space-64);
    }
  }
</style>
